1.As a user I want to have a ready tutorial which shows how to use that software.
2.As a user I want to see on a board what I can do with this software.
3. As a user I want to choose a image from my files of which I want to verify the specie. 
4. As a user I want the results in a pdf file which will include the image and the result. 
5. As a user I want to choose my files from the library with the mouse. 
6. As a user I want to know how much time does it take to verify any particular image. 
7. As a user I also want to see at least the last 10 verification results which were done on that software. 
